  "steps": [
    "Heat coconut oil in a non-stick kadai, add asafoetida, mustard seeds and split black gram, mix and once the mustard seeds begin to splutter, add dried red chillies, green chillies and curry leaves, mix and sauté for 1 minute.",
    "Add sprouted green gram and salt, mix and cook for 6-8 minutes on medium heat.",
    "Add scraped coconut and mix well.",
    "Transfer into a serving bowl and serve hot."
